<p>The Centre for Soldiers' Wives &amp; Mothers,<br/>92B. Pitt Street, Sydney.<br/>28-2-16</p>
<p>Dear M. Horsefield<br/>Could you assist Mrs. Lock with her debt which is pressing. She will show you the bill &ndash; Her husband is only allowing her 3/- p. day so her pay for self &amp; 1 child is not quite to scale &ndash;</p>
<p>Yours faithfully<br/>B. Booth &ndash;</p>
